  "bio_raw": "Md. Zesun Ahmed Mia has been working as Lecturer, Department of Electrical and Electronic Engineering (EEE) at University of Liberal Arts Bangladesh (ULAB), Dhaka, Bangladesh since February, 2021.\nHe completed his B.Sc. in Electrical and Electronic Engineering (EEE) from Bangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET), Dhaka in 2019. He is currently pursuing his M.Sc. in EEE in BUET. He has worked as a lecturer in the department of EEE of Bangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET) from February, 2020 to January 2021. Before this, he was a lecturer of Prime University since his graduation in 2019 to February, 2020. He has been a member of IEEE since 2015 and has also participated in and won various robotics competitions from 2016 to 2018.",
  "stated_interests": [
    "Machine Learning, Nanoelectronics, VLSI, Device Technology, 2D Materials."
  ],
  "education": [
    {
      "raw": "Education\n(ongoing) M.Sc. in Electrical and Electronic Engineering (EEE)\nin Bangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET)\nB.Sc. in Electrical and Electronic Engineering (EEE)\nin Bangladesh University of Engineering and Technology (BUET)."
